description: List Bring Your Own License (BYOL) subscription registration resources for your account.

parameters.name: SubscriptionProviderSources
parameters.description: To filter your results, specify which subscription providers to return in the list. (string) ---

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The next token used for paginated responses. When this field isn't empty, there are additional elements that the service hasn't included in this request. Use this token with the next request to retrieve additional objects.

nested_items.name: RegisteredSubscriptionProviders
nested_items.description: The list of BYOL registration resources that fit the criteria you specified in the request.

nested_items.name: LastSuccessfulDataRetrievalTime
nested_items.description: The timestamp from the last time that License Manager accessed third-party subscription data for your account from your registered Linux subscription provider.

nested_items.name: SecretArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Secrets Manager secret that stores your registered Linux subscription provider access token. For RHEL account subscriptions, this is the offline token.

nested_items.name: SubscriptionProviderArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Linux subscription provider resource that you registered.

nested_items.name: SubscriptionProviderSource
nested_items.description: A supported third-party Linux subscription provider. License Manager currently supports Red Hat subscriptions.

nested_items.name: SubscriptionProviderStatus
nested_items.description: Indicates the status of your registered Linux subscription provider access token from the last time License Manager retrieved subscription data. For RHEL account subscriptions, this is the status of the offline token.

nested_items.name: SubscriptionProviderStatusMessage
nested_items.description: A detailed message that's associated with your BYOL subscription provider token status.
